title: Episode 302: He's a Runner...Out this Interview (Feat. Mooski)
itunes:title: Episode 302: He's a Runner...Out this Interview (Feat. Mooski)
description:
Hip Hop artist, Mooski joins the ladies of Lip Service this week to promote the remix to his smash hit "Trackstar." It's safe to say about 20 minutes into this episode...Mooski didn't know what he got himself involved in. Mooski opens up about a pregnancy scare he had while serving the US Military in Japan, how he wants to marry the lady he's currently with, growing up in the church, and much more. Enjoy!
